#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/pxl-outline.c:81
msgid "Selection to Path"
msgstr "Výber do cesty"

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:142
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:143
msgid "Converts a selection to a path"
msgstr "Prevedie výber na cestu"

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:151
msgid "_Align Threshold"
msgstr "_Prah zarovnania"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:152
msgid "If two endpoints are closer than this, they are made to be equal."
msgstr ""
"Ak sú dva krajné body bližšie ako toto nastavenie, nastavia sa na rovnakú "
"hodnotu."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:158
msgid "Corner Al_ways Threshold"
msgstr "Prah istoty _rohu"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:159
msgid ""
"If the angle defined by a point and its predecessors and successors is "
"smaller than this, it's a corner, even if it's within 'corner_surround' "
"pixels of a point with a smaller angle."
msgstr ""
"Ak je uhol definovaný bodom a jeho predchodcami a nástupcami menší ako táto "
"hodnota, ide o roh. A to aj keď je v rámci „Okolie rohu“ pixelov od bodu s "
"menším uhlom."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:167
msgid "Corner _Surround"
msgstr "_Okolie rohu"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:168
msgid ""
"Number of points to consider when determining if a point is a corner or not."
msgstr ""
"Počet bodov, ktoré sa majú zohľadniť pri určovaní, či je bod rohom alebo nie."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:174
msgid "Cor_ner Threshold"
msgstr "_Prah rohu"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:175
msgid ""
"If a point, its predecessors, and its successors define an angle smaller "
"than this, it's a corner."
msgstr ""
"Ak bod, jeho predchodcovia a nástupcovia definujú uhol menší ako toto, ide o "
"roh."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:181
msgid "Error Thres_hold"
msgstr "P_rah chyby"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:182
msgid ""
"Amount of error at which a fitted spline is unacceptable. If any pixel is "
"further away than this from the fitted curve, we try again."
msgstr ""
"Veľkosť chyby, pri ktorom je prispôsobená krivka neprijateľná. Ak je "
"akýkoľvek pixel vzdialenejší od prispôsobenej krivky ako táto hodnota, pokus "
"sa zopakuje."

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:189
msgid "_Filter Alternative Surround"
msgstr "_Filtrovať alternatívne okolie"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:190
msgid "A second number of adjacent points to consider when filtering."
msgstr "Druhý počet susedných bodov, ktoré sa majú zohľadniť pri filtrovaní."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:196
msgid "Filter E_psilon"
msgstr "Filtrovať E_psilon"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:197
msgid ""
"If the angles between the vectors produced by filter_surround and "
"filter_alternative_surround points differ by more than this, use the one "
"from filter_alternative_surround."
msgstr ""
"Ak sa uhly medzi vektormi vytvorenými bodmi Filtrovať_popredie a "
"Filtrovať_alternatívne_popredie líšia o viac ako túto hodnotu, je bod rohom."

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:205
msgid "Filter Iteration Co_unt"
msgstr "Počet ite_rácií filtra"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:206
msgid ""
"Number of times to smooth original data points.  Increasing this number "
"dramatically --- to 50 or so --- can produce vastly better results. But if "
"any points that 'should' be corners aren't found, the curve goes to hell "
"around that point."
msgstr ""
"Počet vyhladzovaní pôvodných dátových bodov. Dramatické zvýšenie tohto čísla "
"--- o približne 50 --- môže priniesť výrazne lepšie výsledky. Ak sa však "
"nenájdu žiadne body, ktoré by „mali“ byť rohy, krivka sa v tom bode úplne "
"pokazí."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:215
msgid "Filt_er Percent"
msgstr "_Percento filtra"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:216
msgid ""
"To produce the new point, use the old point plus this times the neighbors."
msgstr ""
"Na vytvorenie nového bodu použiť starý bod plus takýto násobok susedov."

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:222
msgid "Filter Secondar_y Surround"
msgstr "F_iltrovať sekundárne popredie"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:223
msgid ""
"Number of adjacent points to consider if 'filter_surround' points defines a "
"straight line."
msgstr ""
"Počet susedných bodov, ktoré sa majú zohľadniť, ak body „Filtrovať_popredie” "
"definujú priamku."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:229
msgid "Filter Surroun_d"
msgstr "_Filtrovať popredie"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:230
msgid "Number of adjacent points to consider when filtering."
msgstr "Počet susedných bodov, ktoré sa majú zohľadniť pri filtrovaní."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:235
msgid "_Keep Knees"
msgstr "_Ponechať kolená"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:236
msgid "Says whether or not to remove 'knee' points after finding the outline."
msgstr ""
"Udáva, či sa majú po nájdení obrysu odstrániť „kolenné“ body alebo nie."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:242
msgid "_Line Reversion Threshold"
msgstr "_Prah vrátenia riadka"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:243
msgid ""
"If a spline is closer to a straight line than this, it remains a straight "
"line, even if it would otherwise be changed back to a curve. This is "
"weighted by the square of the curve length, to make shorter curves more "
"likely to be reverted."
msgstr ""
"Ak je krivka bližšie k priamke ako táto hodnota, zostane priamkou, aj keď by "
"inak mohla byť zmenená späť na krivku. Toto je vážené štvorcom dĺžky krivky, "
"aby sa zvýšila pravdepodobnosť, že kratšie krivky budú vrátené späť."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:252
msgid "L_ine Threshold"
msgstr "Prah č_iary"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:253
msgid ""
"How many pixels (on the average) a spline can diverge from the line "
"determined by its endpoints before it is changed to a straight line."
msgstr ""
"Koľko pixelov (v priemere) sa môže krivka odchýliť od priamky určenej jej "
"krajnými bodmi, kým sa zmení na priamku."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:260
msgid "Reparametri_ze Improvement"
msgstr "_Vylepšenie opätovnej parametrizácie"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:261
msgid ""
"If reparameterization doesn't improve the fit by this much percent, stop "
"doing it. Amount of error at which it is pointless to reparameterize."
msgstr ""
"Ak zmena parametrov nezlepší zhodu o tento počet percent, prestať ju "
"vykonávať. Veľkosť chyby, pri ktorej už opätovná parametrizácia nedáva "
"zmysel."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:268
msgid "Repara_metrize Threshold"
msgstr "Prah _opätovnej parametrizácie"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:269
msgid ""
"Amount of error at which it is pointless to reparameterize.  This happens, "
"for example, when we are trying to fit the outline of the outside of an 'O' "
"with a single spline. The initial fit is not good enough for the Newton-"
"Raphson iteration to improve it.  It may be that it would be better to "
"detect the cases where we didn't find any corners."
msgstr ""
"Veľkosť chyby, pri ktorej nemá zmysel vykonávať opätovnú parametrizáciu. K "
"tomu dochádza napríklad vtedy, keď sa snažíme prispôsobiť obrys vonkajšej "
"strany písmena ‚O‘ pomocou jedinej krivky. Počiatočné prispôsobenie nie je "
"dostatočne dobré na to, aby ho Newtonova-Raphsonova iterácia mohla vylepšiť. "
"Možno by bolo lepšie zistiť prípady, v ktorých sme nenašli žiadne rohy."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:279
msgid "Subdi_vide Search"
msgstr "_Rozdeliť hľadanie"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:280
msgid ""
"Percentage of the curve away from the worst point to look for a better place "
"to subdivide."
msgstr ""
"Percentuálny úsek krivky od najhoršieho bodu, na ktorom treba hľadať "
"vhodnejšie miesto na rozdelenie."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:286
msgid "Su_bdivide Surround"
msgstr "R_ozdeliť okolie"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:287
msgid ""
"Number of points to consider when deciding whether a given point is a better "
"place to subdivide."
msgstr ""
"Počet bodov, ktoré sa majú zohľadniť pri rozhodovaní, či je daný bod lepším "
"miestom na rozdelenie."

# label pri slideri
#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:293
msgid "Subdivide Th_reshold"
msgstr "Prah pre ro_zdelenie"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:294
msgid ""
"How many pixels a point can diverge from a straight line and still be "
"considered a better place to subdivide."
msgstr ""
"Koľko pixelov sa môže bod odchýliť od priamky a stále bude považovaný za "
"lepšie miesto na rozdelenie."

#
#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:301
msgid "_Tangent Surround"
msgstr "_Tangenciálne okolie"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:302
msgid ""
"Number of points to look at on either side of a point when computing the "
"approximation to the tangent at that point."
msgstr ""
"Počet bodov, ktoré sa majú zohľadniť na oboch stranách daného bodu pri "
"výpočte aproximácie tangenty v tomto bode."

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:324
msgid "No selection to convert"
msgstr "Nie je žiadny výber na konverziu"

#: plug-ins/selection-to-path/selection-to-path.c:361
msgid "Selection to Path Advanced Settings"
msgstr "Rozšírené nastavenia výberu na cesty"

